# KevinK.dev Public API

The KevinK.dev Public API allows anyone to pull data from KevinK.dev without any need to pay or register.

## Blogging Module [/blog]

### Get Newest Post [GET/blog/{locale}/newest]

Get the newest post in your preferred locale. If that locale is not available the system will fallback to english.

+ Parameters
    + locale: `en` (string) - Any supported locale.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

